omnishell (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Replace monolithic registry with layered core under src/core/registry/
    (IRegistry, LocalRegistry, JsonRegistry, VolumeRegistry, RegistryService).
  * Add authentication abstractions (os::auth) and wx PasswordManager proxy
    with LoginDialog and in-memory PasswordDb.
  * Standardize built-in apps on App + Frame + Body; add Browser, Connect4,
    Sudoku, Chain, Solitaire, FiveOrMore; refactor Control Panel and
    Minesweeper accordingly.
  * Shell chrome updates (desktop, taskbar, start menu, LabeledIcon).

